{"tid":994852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議員查看輸入中國人計劃分類圖表　「其他」一項排第一　非常古怪","createTime":"2019-01-25T04:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T07:47:35.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4298d8651551d9be22e18eae41dcc612ebe1f7","tid":994852,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/輸入內地人才計劃的首五類獲分配名額行業/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%96%E4%BA%94%E9%A1%9E%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%2F&d=0R25PRPV8%2Bl%2F0TdEluToSjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=da6e1987\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%96%E4%BA%94%E9%A1%9E%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%90%8D%E9%A1%8D%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%2F&h=cb0e258a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/輸入內地人才計劃的首五類獲分配名額行業/</a><br />\n<br />\n本欄前文整理了有關各類申請入境香港居留或就業計劃的數據，其中以輸入內地人才計劃的獲分配名額最高。<br />\n<br />\n第三和第五高的行業分別為金融服務和商業及貿易，但第四高的行業卻是無以名狀，統稱為「其他」。本來統計總不能完全分類，總有「其他」一項，但有趣是這「其他」一項由2008年只有1宗，至2017年急升150倍，增至1504宗。一般而言，當「其他」一項的數量增加至第四高，表示有些未分類的行業必須獨立分類，以反映該等行業的實際狀況及影響。<br />\n<br />\n相類似的情況在一般就業計劃同樣出現，圖2 為一般就業計劃內的獲分配名額的首五類行業，2017年的大約4萬名獲分配名額當中，最高人數的行業竟然是「其他」，達到13,252人，約佔三份一！在統計分析中出現「其他」一項成為最高類別可謂難得一見，對分析既沒有幫助，更把問題隱藏，公眾難以監察政策。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0b_9tT2B_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0b_9tT2B_1200x0.jpg&h=7ad940e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83351d8f3bca777ecf837436ecf3c1a8f62fc813","tid":994852,"uid":93986,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"因為尼班人跟本無業。"},{"pid":"8b614f369addead573a7be7b141454cce525031d","tid":994852,"uid":232815,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但有趣是這「其他」一項由2008年只有1宗，至2017年急升150倍，增至1504宗。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b3bb52fb4969b11a30017c1256197772a867e1","tid":994852,"uid":9726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"690d19b6638b8d60daf8f88caffdc1427edd6adf","tid":994852,"uid":1643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"果項係咪無業/大媽舞/走私？"},{"pid":"e20b03a652e83658821259076594e7dff233ab90","tid":994852,"uid":193893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"690d19b6638b8d60daf8f88caffdc1427edd6adf","tid":994852,"uid":1643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"果項係咪無業/大媽舞/走私？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:34:54.000Z","msg":"七日鮮同神秘房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb2c39e6ada6d9121ec07f186c0e21a09b61cb6","tid":994852,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a8c5ab3225c2ec508b2ff9ba6c3b1840de6a5d","tid":994852,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"事但啦個個都知咩事但冇人會理"},{"pid":"ca23ca53bebdc0ea15d3c7bfc2493dbfca0bf27f","tid":994852,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"世界上有兩大強國<br />\n第一個係美國<br />\n第二個係其他國家<br />\n完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}